text: Edmundo Eluchans Urenda (born 21 January 1950) is a Chilean politician who served as President of the Chamber of Deputies and as a member of the Chamber of Deputies, representing Districts 14 and 15 of the Valparaíso Region. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of the Chamber of Deputies of Chile Category:Independent Democratic Union politicians Category:Pontifical Catholic University of Chile alumni
title: Edmundo Eluchans
